### Installation 

```bash
pip install rbom
```

### Signing 

Generate RSA Key Pair 

```bash
openssl genrsa -out private_rbom_key.pem 2048
openssl rsa -in private_rbom_key.pem -pubout -out public_rbom_key.pem
```


